WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:03.960
The Barclays app

2
00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.800
How to make an international payment

3
00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:15.680
To make an international payment, tap
'Pay & Transfer' at the bottom of your screen.

4
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:20.160
Next select 'International payment'.

5
00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:23.520
Now choose the account you
want to make the payment from.

6
00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:28.520
Enter the amount you
want to send in pounds.

7
00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:32.320
Select the currency
you want to make the payment in

8
00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:37.200
and the exchange rate with the converted
amount will appear here.

9
00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:39.360
Tap 'Continue'.

10
00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:43.120
Now enter the recipient's details

11
00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:48.800
and select the country they're based in.

12
00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:57.440
Next, add their International Bank
Account Number, or IBAN.

13
00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:03.760
Then tap 'Continue'.

14
00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:07.040
Here, you can check your payment summary.

15
00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:10.360
Here, you'll see if a fee is chargeable.

16
00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:14.960
International payments made through the
app are free from Barclays charges.

17
00:01:15.160 --> 00:01:20.120
However, some countries allow the bank
receiving the payment to charge a fee.

18
00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:24.000
The sender must pay the fee
if it's sent by our app.

19
00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:27.120
Add a reference for your statement here

20
00:01:30.520 --> 00:01:32.600
and for the recipient here.

21
00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:36.640
Tap 'Review payment'.

22
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:43.640
Now, for security, you'll need to enter
the last three digits

23
00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:47.640
on the back of your bank card
and your card expiry date.

24
00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:50.760
Then tap 'Confirm'.

25
00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:54.280
And your payment will be submitted.

